Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:03.86,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So, when are you guys going to have the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:05.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When I have enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:09.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Why did you marry a poor guy like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:11.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Because I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:14.29,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't be so frank about it; you'll make me depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:18.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll be calling you "Father" from now, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:19.98,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,No way! You'll creep me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But you are my father-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:24.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,right, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:30.51,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Then I'll call you "Son" from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:31.81,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,All right, Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:35.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Stop that, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:36.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:36.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:40.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.58,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Son!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:37.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Son!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:17.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:18.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:22.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to say at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:25.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Say what about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:29.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Today's the start of our new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Should I be saying, "Ready, set, go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:35.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That'd be strange, since there's no finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Since we're going to be living together by supporting each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,it's probably, "Please take good care of me."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:52.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to make an oath between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,An oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.48,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I, Okazaki Nagisa, will not cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:02.48,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No matter the hardship, I will overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:08.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But I may cry in happy situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This is who I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,...but I hope you will take good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Same here. I hope you'll take good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:29.81,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,413.1)}Episode 14
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:29.81,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,696.6)}A New Family
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:45.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is it really all right for me to get in the bath first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:50.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. I'll get in first tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:54.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay. Then I'll take a dip first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:07.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Calm down. I've heard the sound of Nagisa showering in that house many times. {ep13}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! {ep13}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:13.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Cold water came out... {ep13}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, it takes a while before hot water comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:21.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Start it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, I'll try to get out fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry; take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:37.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I can't do that. You have work tomorrow, so you have to go to bed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:38.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:49.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll start looking for a job tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:50.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:57.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,A job. I can't be doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you serious about working?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:17.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. Of course, I won't neglect the household chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:20.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,After all, this is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:27.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll do chores around the house, too. But, is your body holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:35.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I am physically weak, but I don't want to be a weak person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:41.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry; I'm being selfish again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:44.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:47.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've never wished for anything grand in your life, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:52.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm always asking a lot from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:59.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All you ever ask for are things like playing baseball with the old man and holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:25.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're married, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:32.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet lots of things will happen to us from here on;\Namazing things and painful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But I'll be able to face them as long as I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:41.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Same here. As long as you're with me,\NI think I can handle anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:45.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So make sure you always stay by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:52.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll always be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:59.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is how Nagisa and my new life started. {ep13}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I needed to support the lives of two people starting that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:09.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But rather than a burden, to me, it was joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When I got off from work, I headed straight for home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To the home where Nagisa waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:46.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I called Nishina-san today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:50.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She gave me her phone number at the graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She wasn't admitted to a college, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:56.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No. She's studying now to enter a music school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:08:02.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She said she's working since she didn't want to be a burden on her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wow, good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:09.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I heard she's going to work at\Na family restaurant that opens next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:12.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She asked me if I would like to work with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:13.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,With her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. As a waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:20.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm also looking for a job,\Nso I thought it would be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's better than going to a place full of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:27.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But let the old man and Sanae-san know, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:28.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What's on your mind, Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:43.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What Miyazawa said some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There's a legend from the early days of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:50.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When there are blessed people around, a light appears near them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:57.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was thinking that a light could be around us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If we get a hold of a light,\Nwe can have a wish granted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What would you ask for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've got to have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Really, I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Actually, there is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:19.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really? What is it? If you say it, I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,A baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:26.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:38.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.76,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Welco- Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.99,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's you brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I got out early, so I had some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:49.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I thought I'd show my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.95,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Really? This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:57.48,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this opportunity the last couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:09:59.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.49,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We're going to go see Nagisa work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:12.86,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What kind of guy goes into a family restaurant alone and orders a chocolate parfait?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why should I care? And why a chocolate parfait?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:19.24,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You haven't gone to the restaurant Nagisa works at, yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:22.23,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You don't want to see her in her waitress uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:27.65,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:33.85,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But if I get caught taking pictures as her father, I'd be a laughingstock of the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:38.12,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So I'm going as your friend #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'll be found out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.53,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'll only look like a strange rapper to those who don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,YO! YO! I'm the MC Akio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.66,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'm holding the mike and am the invincible baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're totally giving yourself away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:55.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Seriously? You mean that? Crap, Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Whatever. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.13,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Bro, wait, Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:22.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This place used to be a grove; it was full of trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.44,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Man, things can really change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.25,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:35.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:46.72,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Welcom- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:48.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.57,Default,Rie,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.37,Default,Rie,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.38,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,An anonymous rapper, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.15,Default,Rie,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.92,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Rie-chan, the manager's looking this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.85,Default,Rie,0,0,0,,Two customers. This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:14.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Glad to see this place so lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:17.63,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I bet this area will change a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:21.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What's with that crappy face of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Welcome, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:38.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, I got some free time, so I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:44.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I heard from Nishina-san and Sugisaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is he your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't recognize him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:54.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, this is my first time meeting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Here's the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.29,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,See? She couldn't tell it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like father, like daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.82,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Leave the compliment at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Are you ready to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll have a hot coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He'll have a parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The biggest one you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:28.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,One order of hot coffee and one chocolate and strawberry mix parfait diamond special.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll be back with them shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.66,Default,Waiter,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:37.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Why do I have to eat something as fancy as this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to have a parfait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Did I ever utter a single word of wanting to eat one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You said out loud that you wanted one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:48.69,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:57.02,Default,Rie,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san is very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.91,Default,Rie,0,0,0,,There seem to be customers who come here wanting to see her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.48,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Rie-chan, she's no longer Furukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:08.07,Default,Rie,0,0,0,,Oh right. She's Okazaki Nagisa-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.33,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'd call it uniform magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.88,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,She does look extra cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.36,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Rie-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.54,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, what time do you get off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:26.16,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I'll treat you to dinner, so let's go eat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:29.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll have to go straight home after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:34.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I need to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.83,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:37.74,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:38.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.04,Default,Rie,0,0,0,,"Go"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:40.87,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:43.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We won't start any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.59,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Come on. Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.20,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:51.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's been years; I never expected to see you in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.78,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You're disturbing the other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:58.13,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Step outside, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:02.91,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm never coming back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.91,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.46,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Damn, they got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:12.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The manager wants to see you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:13.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:18.13,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'll leave the problems to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:20.12,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Bye bye boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:26.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:30.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I was happy that you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:35.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But when I think about you getting yelled at by the manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:41.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't tell him that you're my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I don't want you to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:52.68,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Your wife is a very hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He knows already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:57.53,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Nishina-kun and Sugisaka-kun told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:01.38,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I wanted to greet you since it was a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:04.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:08.60,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Oh no. After all, your precious wife was being accosted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.32,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I can imagine what you must have felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:16.70,Default,Man,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, something similar happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:20.79,Default,Man,0,0,0,,That time, she handled the situation well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Handled the situation? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:30.34,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Apparently she's physically weak and has no work experience, but she's smart and has a strong mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:34.55,Default,Man,0,0,0,,People like her are crucial to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:40.43,Default,Man,0,0,0,,But she is too serious; she is easily depressed when she makes a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.69,Default,Man,0,0,0,,so at times like that, please take care of her at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:48.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I will. Thank you for all your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:54.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please keep watching over Nagi- I mean, my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.58,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Likewise. It's a pleasure to have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looks like you found yourself a new place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:07.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. It reminds me of the days I was working hard with the Theater Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You looked good in the uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:13.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My friend #1 said you looked cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:19.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I-I'm not cute. Nishina-san and Sugisaka-san are much cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I just remembered something Nishina-san told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:29.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Apparently a new building's going to be built at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They're going to tear down the old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:39.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,New students two years from now will get to study in brand new classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's a great thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's not good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:10.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:18.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It didn't sound like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:21.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to apologize if I said something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What made you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It just made me upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:36.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That old building has the Theater Club's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's the place where we worked hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:49.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll miss that building when it goes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:56.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry, I think I'm being touchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:03.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, it was thoughtless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:07.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:20.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was really out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:25.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why do I feel so uneasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The city's changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:36.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Both Nagisa and I... and everything around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:41.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And, when everything completely changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:47.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even so, can you keep on loving this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Look, they're finally printed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:02.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When did you take all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.87,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I went back many times after that and took these!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I put much work into these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,At times, I'd be belly down on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:17.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,On other times, I'd be hidden in the kitchen and aim for an acrobatic angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm surprised they didn't kick you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.48,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What are the girls up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.19,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I want to show off my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:29.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't know. But Nagisa said she wanted to ask Sanae-san something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey wait, you're going to show them the pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:36.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nagisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:39.99,San,San,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:42.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I just felt sick for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.06,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What? Are you pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Have some tact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:55.54,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Actually, if you were a man, she should be by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.08,San,San,0,0,0,,Looks like she is pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.11,Default,2,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.49,San,San,0,0,0,,A baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:03.99,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Whose? Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.56,San,San,0,0,0,,It's Nagisa and Tomoya-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.01,San,San,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:12.63,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute, Sanae! A baby, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.37,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Did a bird drop one off for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Or did she pick one up in a cabbage patch?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:22.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,N-No, Dad. Tomoya-kun and I are married, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wait, she isn't going to say it, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,...we are doing dirty things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:38.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To say this so frankly to her parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:41.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She must be a rare animal on this Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:48.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She hasn't had her period, so I'm pretty sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:52.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.93,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:01.09,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:03.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...
