Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:42.18,San,San,0,0,0,,This is Yagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.75,0:23:46.26,San,San,0,0,0,,She is my friend and works as a midwife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:48.87,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,I'm Yagi. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:50.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm Okazaki Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.64,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
